Kitsune is a simple prototype based programming language.

Goals:

Compiles to C for portability
Reasonably Fast (within an order of magnitude times slower than C)
Have fun creating a new programming language (fun)
Has a good/complete standard library with a focus on games



Requirements:

libgc -> http://www.hpl.hp.com/personal/Hans_Boehm/gc/
scons -> http://www.scons.org/


Compiles on:

Mac OS X 10.5 and libgc 7.1
Ubuntu 9.04 and libgc 6.8


If you like this code, have questions or have used it in an interesting way feel free to email me at seoushi@gmail.com .


